text: Caseyidae is a family of millipedes in the order Chordeumatida. There are about 7 genera and at least 40 described species in Caseyidae. ==Genera== * Caseya Cook & Collins, 1895 * Metopiona Gardner & Shelley, 1989 * Ochrogramma Gardner & Shelley, 1989 * Opiona Chamberlin, 1951 * Speoseya Causey, 1954 * Underwoodia Cook & Collins, 1895 * Vasingtona Chamberlin, 1941 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * Category:Chordeumatida Category:Millipede families
title: Caseyidae
